    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler sig-EasyLife SIG 是什么？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler sig-EasyLife SIG（Special Interest Group，特别兴趣小组）负责 Some tools to improve the operation efficiency of the openEuler community.。该 SIG 共有 11 名核心成员，维护 19 个代码仓库，属于 基础设施与工具 领域。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "如何参与 openEuler sig-EasyLife SIG？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "参与 openEuler sig-EasyLife SIG 的方式：1）向相关仓库（如 src-openeuler/openEuler-Advisor、openeuler/openEuler-Advisor、openeuler/li-wen）提交 Pull Request；2）订阅邮件列表 dev@openeuler.org；3）参加 SIG 定期工作会议，会议信息见 openEuler 官网活动日历。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler sig-EasyLife SIG 包含哪些代码仓库？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler sig-EasyLife SIG 共维护 19 个代码仓库，主要包括：src-openeuler/openEuler-Advisor、openeuler/openEuler-Advisor、openeuler/li-wen 等。完整列表见 https://www.openeuler.org/zh/sig/sig-EasyLife。"
        }
      },
